# License

Unlike other hackathon projects, this solution is not a fork or a copy of any existing repositories. The resilience architecture (Graceful Degradation), the orchestration engine based on Semantic Kernel, and the processing logic have been designed from scratch as a piece of proprietary engineering.

🚫 Anti-Fork Usage Restrictions

- Prohibition of unauthorized forks: Any duplication, distribution, or commercial use of the source code contained in this repository is strictly prohibited without the prior express written consent of the author.
- Architecture rights: All rights over the failover logic and the system design are not available for free use. Any attempt to recreate this variant under another name, whether partially or fully, will be considered an infringement of intellectual property rights.

